name: Montgomery Blair High School Smart Phone Programming Club
body:
# Projects.
### Speed Trig
![Speed Trig](http://tinyurl.com/speedTrigLauncher)
Speed Trig is an application designed to help users improve their ability to compute basic trigonometric functions by practicing with digital quizzes on the unit circle. You can visit our [Speed Trig Android Repository](https://github.com/MBHS-SPC/speed-trig-android) or our [Speed Trig iOS Repository](https://github.com/MBHS-SPC/speed-trig-ios). The app can be found on the [Android play store](https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=edu.mbhs.speedtrig)  

### Blair Talks
![Blair Talks](http://tinyurl.com/BlairTalksIcon2)
Blair Talks allows people to see their favorite teachers and hear their catchphrases. You can visit our [Blair Talks Android Repository](https://github.com/MBHS-SPC/blair-talks-android) or our [Blair Talks iOS Repository](https://github.com/MBHS-SPC/Blair-Talks-ios). The app can be found on the [Android Play store](https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=edu.mbhs.blairtalks) and the [Apple App Store](https://itunes.apple.com/us/app/blair-talks/id1052362386?mt=8)  

# Support or Contact
Have trouble? Contact spc.mbhs@gmail.com
